  "description": [
    "Of Interest to Members of the Tabernacle Soci ety are urged to attend Benedic tion of the Blessed Sacrament Wednesday Feb 16 in the Convent chapel of the Sisters of Notre Dame 331 E Rich St Father George Fulcher assistant pastor at St Joseph Cathedral and spiritual director of the society will be cele brant The Altar and Rosary society and PTA of Our Lady of Peace parish will sponsor a Valentine potluck dinner Sunday Feb 13 in the school hall from 500 to 800 pm A social and games party will follow the supper and the public is invited Mrs Alfred DelBianco of the Altar and Ro sary society and Mrs John Oli ver of the PTA will serve as co chairmen of the supper Assist ing them will be Mrs James Armstrong hostesses Mrs Fred Lorre and Mrs Charles E Ruhl decorations Mrs Hugh Graves games Mrs John Seimer co chairman of games Mrs Stanley Bolek Mrs Don Cox and Mrs George Bod ish refreshments Mrs Raymond Connor hospital ity and Mrs Frank Van Holte cochairman of hospitality WHERE THOUSANDS SAVE MILLIONS 07 Current Return a I 0 Account 4 insured To 10000 CENTRAL OHO FEDERAL SAVINGS 78"
